- **理论理解**：{{THEORY_SCORE}}/10
- **实践能力**：{{PRACTICE_SCORE}}/10
- **应变能力**：{{ADAPTABILITY_SCORE}}/10
- **创新思维**：{{INNOVATION_SCORE}}/10

